title: Sexual Fantasy Kingdom Complete to Sept 2013
description:
It has come to my attention that my favorite porn artist is literally a starving artist, so I'm uploading this collection in the hopes of increasing awareness of her work, and hopefully generating some sales from the fellow pirates who have a try-before-you-buy outlook.

Sexual Fantasy Kingdom is a series of "games" set in a fantasy world with various sexual scenes.

These are the uncensored versions.

Included in this torrent:
-- SFK 1: Sex With Creatures
-- SFK 2: Futanari Elves
-- SFK 2: Futanari Elves Galaxy Edition (higher resolution than the original, extra scene)
-- SFK 3: Black Magic
-- SFK 4: Futanari Kingdom
-- Pirate Amnesty (If you're only going to buy one, may as well buy this just for the lulz)
-- The Girl Prince
-- Vampire Halloween

These are all available for download elsewhere, so someone dedicated to obtaining these without paying would be able to regardless.  It's simply my hope to advertise for someone in need.
